{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以黎明，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"與十夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"與偶數和奇數，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"與離去的黑夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"對於有理智者，此中有一種盟誓嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"難道你不知道你的主怎樣懲治阿德人——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"有高柱的伊賴姆人嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"像那樣的人，在別的城市裡還沒有被創造過的——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"怎樣懲治在山谷裡鑿石為家的賽莫德人，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"怎樣懲治有武力的法老。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"這等人曾在國中放肆，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"乃多行不義，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"故你的主把一種刑罰，傾注在他們身上。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你的主，確是監視的。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"至於人，當他的主考驗他，故優待他，而且使他過安逸生活的時候，他說：「我的主優待我了。」"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"當他考驗他，故節約他的給養的時候，他說：「我的主凌辱我了。」"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"絕不然！但你們不優待孤兒，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"你們不以濟貧相勉勵，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你們侵吞遺產，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"你們酷愛錢財。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"絕不然！當大地震動復震動，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你的主的命令，和排班的天神，同齊來臨的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"在那日，火獄將被拿來；在那日，人將覺悟，但覺悟於他有何裨益呢？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他將說：「但願我在世的時候曾行善事。」"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"在那日，任何人，不用他的那種刑罰懲治別人；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"任何人，不用他的那種束縛束縛別人。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"安定的靈魂啊！"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"你應當喜悅地，被喜悅地歸於你的主。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"你應當入在我的眾僕裡；"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"你應當入在我的樂園裡。"}]}